'''Brownlung''' was a disease found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]] and was similar to [[Lung/Legends|lung]] [[cancer]] or [[Wikipedia:Black lung|black lung]]. It was more common in the working classes than in the nobility, mostly because the working classes were forced to live in underground [[turumme-warrens]].

